    java.lang.Cloneable, ExecutionListener, Initializable, Changeable, Debuggable, DebugListener, Derivable, ExceptionHandler, HierarchyListener, ModelErrorHandler, MoMLExportable, Moveable, Nameable
    public class AnalyzeExceptionAttribute
extends CatchExceptionAttribute
    An extension of CatchExceptionAttribute, this attribute catches exceptions and offers ontology analysis. If the exception cannot be handled, the attribute indicates this to the Manager. Status messages may be logged to a file.
    Since:
